high_descs: Turn left and make your way to in front of the stove
Pick up the pan from the left front burner of the stove
Turn right then take a quick right and go as far as the brown chair that is on the right, then turn left and go to the fridge
Chill the pan in the fridge then take the pan out of the fridge
Turn left then take a quick left and go to the white square table in front of the wall
Put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on a table

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the left burner.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the pan in the fridge on the shelf below the lettuce. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Turn around and walk to the kitchen table.
Place the pot on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a table.

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the kitchen stove in the corner of the room to the left
grab a sauce pan off of the front left burner
turn around and walk over to the fridge at the end of the room on the left
place the pan inside of the fridge and let it cool, then take it back out
turn around and walk directly forwards to the small kitchen table ahead
place the pan down on top of the kitchen table
anns.task_desc: place a cooled pan down on top of the kitchen table
